'''Sandstorm Flightknife''' was a unit of [[Adumari]] [[Blade-28 fighter]]s from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]]. The [[Flightknife]] participated in the assault of [[Cartann]] nation during the [[Adumari Civil War]].

When [[Major/Legends|Major]] [[Tycho Celchu/Legends|Tycho Celchu]] was shot down during the battle, Sandstorm Six followed him down.

